Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点\N{\fs12}Let's go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要迟到啦\N{\fs12}We're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣知识  我第一次差点死掉  是在9岁\N{\fs12}Fun fact-- the first time I almost died was at the age of nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而凶器呢\N{\fs12}The murder weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉米·迪安牌香肠\N{\fs12}A Jimmy Dean sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  谢尔顿对我做鬼脸\N{\fs12}Mom, Sheldon's making faces at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿\N{\fs12}Sheldon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得替迪安先生说一句  -宝贝\N{\fs12}- In fairness to Mr. Dean... - Honey! 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天早晨  我决定不执行我的嚼20口规矩\N{\fs12}...this one morning, I decided to forgo my normal 20 chews per bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚼20下是美国医学会的建议\N{\fs12}as prescribed by the American Medical Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治  来帮忙\N{\fs12}George, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子过来  没事的  我来帮你打出来\N{\fs12}Come here, boy. We got it. We just got to smack it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生活中任何危机发生时  我家人们\N{\fs12}To further complicate matters, in any real-life crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会像无头苍蝇般恐慌  把事情越搞越糟\N{\fs12}my family's default mode is mindless panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿要死了  谢尔顿要死了\N{\fs12}Sheldon's gonna die! Sheldon's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是漠不关心\N{\fs12}Or heartless apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊\N{\fs12}Oh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  应该这样\N{\fs12}Here we go. This is how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-来吧  我们摇起来  -宝贝\N{\fs12}- Here we go. And we shake. - Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的生命渐渐从身体流失时\N{\fs12}It's interesting the things you think about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所想的东西其实挺有意思\N{\fs12}when life is ebbing from your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  油地毯  这到底是什么啊\N{\fs12}For instance, linoleum. What is it, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塑料吗  那跟福米加塑料贴面差别在哪\N{\fs12}Plastic? And if so, how is it different from Formica?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打紧急求助电话\N{\fs12}I'm calling 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那巧古拉伯爵呢\N{\fs12}And what about Count Chocula?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么是伯爵\N{\fs12}How is he a count?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的爵位是有土地的吗\N{\fs12}Did the title come with land?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治  海姆立克法\N{\fs12}George, Heimlich!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别伤到他的小肋骨\N{\fs12}Don't hurt his little ribs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.31,0:01:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们说  在人生最后关头\N{\fs12}They say, in the final moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一生会在你眼前飞过\N{\fs12}your life passes before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我眼里只看到了我哥舔了果酱刀\N{\fs12}All I saw was my brother licking jelly off the knife
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又伸进去果酱里\N{\fs12}and putting it back in the jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在好了  谢尔顿\N{\fs12}Okay, it's better now. Sheldon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  你没事吧\N{\fs12}Honey. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能呼吸了吗  你说话啊\N{\fs12}Can you breathe? Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得把...  那瓶果酱...  丢掉...\N{\fs12}You have to... throw away... that jelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没上学迟到过\N{\fs12}I've never been late to school before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整天迟到  这都不是事儿\N{\fs12}I'm late all the time. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都准时送你到学校  你为什么迟到了\N{\fs12}I get you to school on time every day. Why are you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都有很多人要跟我请安\N{\fs12}I have a lot of people to say hi to in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈\N{\fs12}Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我写个解释信吗\N{\fs12}would you write a note for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有最酷的迟到理由\N{\fs12}You have the coolest excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差点就死了  你有看到耶稣吗\N{\fs12}You almost died. Did you see Jesus?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到巧古拉伯爵\N{\fs12}I saw Count Chocula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你要写有关我的濒死经历我也不介意\N{\fs12}But feel free to mention my brush with death in the note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  别再说什么死不死的了\N{\fs12}All right, that's enough talk about death and dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就差这么一点点就能有自己的房间了\N{\fs12}I came this close to having my own room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善心捐食物的活动这周五截止\N{\fs12}Remember, the food drive ends Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎捐赠任何罐装食品\N{\fs12}All canned goods are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但拜托大家捐的罐头都有内容物标示\N{\fs12}But please... make sure your cans have labels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有需要的人们  生活已经够烦了\N{\fs12}Needy people have enough problems
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再给他们添麻烦  得猜自己的晚饭是什么了\N{\fs12}without having to guess what's for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我迟到了  我有解释信\N{\fs12}I'm sorry I'm late. I have a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的小家伙  你出了医疗紧急事故吗\N{\fs12}You poor thing, you had a medical emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的老师  我被香肠噎到了\N{\fs12}Yes, ma'am. I choked on a sausage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多大根\N{\fs12}How big was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大根\N{\fs12}About yay big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天\N{\fs12}To this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是没懂他们当时在笑什么\N{\fs12}I still don't understand why they were laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在我的专座上了\N{\fs12}You're sitting in my spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里是你的专座\N{\fs12}Why is it your spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很复杂  你坐过去就是了\N{\fs12}It's complicated. Just move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.71,0:03:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你在读漫画书  -是啊\N{\fs12}- You're reading a comic book. - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道漫画是给小孩看的玩意吧\N{\fs12}You do understand those are for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你读过吗\N{\fs12}Have you ever read one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我三岁时就不屑读图画书了\N{\fs12}I outgrew picture books when I was three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃你的饭就是了\N{\fs12}Just eat your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我没办法吃这个\N{\fs12}I-I don't think I can eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想交换吗\N{\fs12}You want to trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈又给我做了鱼汤\N{\fs12}My mom made me fish soup again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家得住在这国家多少年\N{\fs12}How long do we have to be in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈才能让我吃美式大香肠啊\N{\fs12}before I get baloney?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了\N{\fs12}Mm, no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不饿\N{\fs12}I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不饿\N{\fs12}I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话你在越南永远不会听到\N{\fs12}Three words you never hear in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说件好的\N{\fs12}Well, here's something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识洛圣朋先生吗\N{\fs12}You know that Mr. Rosenbloom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.81,0:04:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牛排馆附近开家具店的那个\N{\fs12}with the furniture store over by the steakhouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不认识  -你肯定认识\N{\fs12}- I don't think so. - Oh, sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有遮秃发型的那个希伯来佬\N{\fs12}That Hebrew fella with the comb-over?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说犹太人吗\N{\fs12}You mean Jewish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像比较喜欢被叫希伯来佬\N{\fs12}I think they like to be called Hebrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言归正传\N{\fs12}Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他约我去共进晚餐\N{\fs12}he's asked me to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  你怎么回答的\N{\fs12}Well, good for you. What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说让我考虑考虑\N{\fs12}I said I'd have to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好考虑的\N{\fs12}What's to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多啊\N{\fs12}Well, a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是晚饭吃得开心\N{\fs12}I mean, assuming he enjoys dinner, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会想来一勺姥姥当饭后甜点吃\N{\fs12}he might want a scoop of Meemaw for dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  孩子在\N{\fs12}Mom, the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了饭后甜点\N{\fs12}I said dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道我刚才说的是上床吗\N{\fs12}Did you know I was talking about sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看\N{\fs12}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不吃\N{\fs12}Why aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到\N{\fs12}I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿  有时候不同食物会"接触"到一起\N{\fs12}Sometimes the different foods touch each other, Sheldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么大不了\N{\fs12}Not the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我是怕我又噎到\N{\fs12}No, I'm afraid I'll choke again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  不会的\N{\fs12}Oh, honey, that's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  快吃饭\N{\fs12}Go ahead, eat your dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这噎到是怎么回事\N{\fs12}What's all this about choking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿今早差点噎死\N{\fs12}Sheldon almost died this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -对啊\N{\fs12}- What?! - Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸把他倒着抱起来  像番茄酱瓶一样抖\N{\fs12}Dad was shaking him upside down like a ketchup bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可精彩了\N{\fs12}It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得吃东西才行啊  宝贝\N{\fs12}Well, you got to eat something, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹吃几口\N{\fs12}Just have a few bites.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  太冒险了\N{\fs12}I can't. It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的炸薯球我要了\N{\fs12}Dibs on the tater tots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吧  我先帮你包起来\N{\fs12}All right, I'll wrap that up for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你晚点饿了  你可以到时候吃\N{\fs12}and if you change your mind, you can have some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹喝了你的牛奶\N{\fs12}At least drink your milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs12}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母看到了\N{\fs12}My mother and father saw
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的幼小心灵收到创伤  对我很有耐心\N{\fs12}that I'd been traumatized and were patient 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也理解我对固体食物感到恐惧\N{\fs12}and understanding about my fear of eating solid foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这状态多维持了一天\N{\fs12}This lasted one more day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿·李·库珀  你再不吃你的猪排\N{\fs12}Sheldon Lee Cooper, if you don't finish that pork chop, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓我就会嚼烂你的猪排\N{\fs12}I swear I will chew it up
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后像只母鸟一样吐到你嘴里喂你\N{\fs12}and spit it in your mouth like a mama bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊  妈  快去\N{\fs12}Do it, Mom. Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  我能跟你聊两句吗\N{\fs12}Mary, can I speak to you for a second? 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  够了就是够了  这孩子得吃东西\N{\fs12}No. Enough is enough. The boy has got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就好\N{\fs12}Just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧开吃  先生\N{\fs12}Start eating, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意给我的吧\N{\fs12}You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把猪排去骨\N{\fs12}How about I cut that pork chop off the bone
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和肉汁一起丢进搅拌机搅碎怎么样\N{\fs12}and throw it in the blender with some gravy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用吸管吸起来  我就喝掉\N{\fs12}If it fits through a bendy straw, I'll drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就弄好\N{\fs12}Coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他凭什么能喝猪排奶昔\N{\fs12}Why does he get a pork shake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怨我\N{\fs12}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天是我催他赶紧把早餐吃完\N{\fs12}I rushed him through breakfast the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你看  他日渐消瘦\N{\fs12}and now look-- he is wasting away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  你不能怪自己\N{\fs12}Oh, come on. You can't blame yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这持续不了多久  还记得有一次蜜蜂飞进屋里\N{\fs12}This isn't gonna last. Remember the time a bee got in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有几个月睡觉都盖着张网吗\N{\fs12}and he slept under a net for a couple months?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不一样\N{\fs12}This is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么个不一样  -\N{\fs12}- How? - First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那蜜蜂是你放进来的\N{\fs12}you let that bee in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错\N{\fs12}The bee was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧  -其次\N{\fs12}- Okay. - Secondly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次关系到他的健康\N{\fs12}this is about his health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个脆弱的小男孩\N{\fs12}He is a fragile little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不能这样下去\N{\fs12}He can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在跟你吵\N{\fs12}I'm not arguing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...  我们就再给他点时间吧\N{\fs12}Let's just, you know, give him a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在搞什么\N{\fs12}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去你妈在弄玛格丽特酒\N{\fs12}Sounds like your mom's making margaritas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在喝什么\N{\fs12}What's he drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪排和肉汁\N{\fs12}Pork chop and gravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还偷偷加了点西兰花\N{\fs12}I snuck some broccoli in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别声张\N{\fs12}Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,255)\fn微软雅黑\fs30\bord0\shad4}五周后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近又开始约会了  我很开心\N{\fs12}I'm real glad you've been getting out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fs12}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们吃了美味的晚餐  散了步\N{\fs12}We had a nice dinner, took a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他离过婚的  你知道吗\N{\fs12}He's a divorcee, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs12}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那种人来说不是大问题\N{\fs12}It's not a big deal for those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就算不是律师  也有当律师的亲戚\N{\fs12}If they're not a lawyer, they're related to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}属于对犹太人的刻板印象  不是律师就是医生会计师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搅拌前还把面包皮去掉啊\N{\fs12}You're actually cutting the crust off before you blend it? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天做金枪鱼三明治时没切  他说喝得出来\N{\fs12}I left it on his tuna sandwich yesterday, he said he could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只喝了一半\N{\fs12}Only drank half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  你觉得这次闹得够久了吗\N{\fs12}Mary, you think this has gone on long enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不麻烦\N{\fs12}No trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是有多一台搅拌机就更好了\N{\fs12}But it'd be better if I had two blenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别再惯着他就更好了\N{\fs12}Be better if you stopped coddling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道还能怎么办\N{\fs12}Well, I don't know what else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提议过带他去看专家\N{\fs12}I suggested that we take him to some kind of professional,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你说他长大就不会这样了\N{\fs12}but you said he'd outgrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想找心理医生\N{\fs12}Well, if you're looking for a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢说我的新男友有亲戚做这行\N{\fs12}I bet my new fella's related to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢\N{\fs12}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不好\N{\fs12}Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们带他去看心理医生\N{\fs12}If we take him to a shrink, 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我们就承认了他有问题\N{\fs12}it feels like we're admitting something's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有五个礼拜没吃过固体食物了\N{\fs12}He hasn't had solid food in five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他真有毛病\N{\fs12}Well, if there is something wrong with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也肯定不会是便秘\N{\fs12}it ain't constipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看能不能找个医生\N{\fs12}Let's see if we can find somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得再加点奇多\N{\fs12}Needs a few more Cheetos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈成功找到了一位我们负担得起的\N{\fs12}My mother managed to locate a family psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭心理医生\N{\fs12}within our price range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没人介意他在《省钱周刊》上\N{\fs12}No one seemed to be bothered that he had
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印有优惠券\N{\fs12}a coupon in The Pennysaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人是不是会逼我吃固体食物\N{\fs12}Is this man gonna make me eat solid foods?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  他只是想和你谈谈\N{\fs12}No, he just wants to talk to you about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没告诉他  我的人生有很多大事要完成\N{\fs12}Did you tell him I have a lot to accomplish in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能被没嚼烂的香肠噎死\N{\fs12}and cannot afford to be killed by an unchewed sausage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了  但用了别种说法\N{\fs12}Not in those exact words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优惠券你带了吗\N{\fs12}Did you bring the coupon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  欢迎\N{\fs12}Hi. Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一定是库珀一家\N{\fs12}You must be the Cooper family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs12}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  好极了\N{\fs12}Right on, right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是谢尔顿了\N{\fs12}This must be Sheldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握个爪吧\N{\fs12}Put 'er there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  谢谢\N{\fs12}No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  好极了\N{\fs12}Right on, right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们先这样  爸爸妈妈\N{\fs12}Okay, well, here's how I'd like to start. Mom and Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先进来和我谈谈  然后  谢尔顿\N{\fs12}why don't you come talk to me first, and then, Sheldon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我再单独唠唠\N{\fs12}you and I have a little rap session.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位\N{\fs12}Folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  好极了\N{\fs12}Right on, right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的漫画你可以随便看\N{\fs12}Feel free to read any of my comics.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以随便坐在我的豆袋椅上\N{\fs12}And you guys feel free to sit on my beanbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4毛钱吗  太离谱了\N{\fs12}40 cents? Outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命运的安排\N{\fs12}As fate would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选的那本漫画叫《X战警》\N{\fs12}the comic I picked up was called X-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有超能力的年少变种人\N{\fs12}Young mutants with incredible powers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被世人恐惧和误解\N{\fs12}who were feared and misunderstood by the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这故事是在讲我\N{\fs12}Hey, it's about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事你得知道\N{\fs12}Now, the thing you have to understand is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢利是个非常聪明的孩子\N{\fs12}Shelly is incredibly bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的智商堪比爱因斯坦\N{\fs12}I mean, his IQ is right up there with Albert Einstein
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和英国那个坐轮椅的人[霍金]\N{\fs12}and that English wheelchair fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -他是一个9岁的高中生\N{\fs12}- Cool. - He's nine years old and he's in high school, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不能把他当寻常孩子看待\N{\fs12}so you can't judge him like other kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-明白了  -乔治\N{\fs12}- I hear ya. - George,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他  谢利总是滔滔不绝\N{\fs12}tell him about how he's always going on and on 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么亚原子粒子的\N{\fs12}about subatomic particles and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能说个没完没了\N{\fs12}Oh, he'll get to gabbin' about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经习惯了他有各种怪癖和奇思妙想\N{\fs12}We're accustomed to his quirks and oddities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但"害怕固体食物"这件事\N{\fs12}But this whole "being afraid of solid foods" thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的让我们懵了\N{\fs12}it's got us thrown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我先说一句\N{\fs12}Okay. Let me just start by saying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来对了地方\N{\fs12}you came to the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿和我碰巧有很多共同之处\N{\fs12}Sheldon and I happen to have a lot in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候也是个特别的男孩\N{\fs12}I, too, was a special little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年级时  我就能读懂七年级的书\N{\fs12}In the fourth grade, I was reading at a seventh grade level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不用告诉你们  七年级时我到什么程度了\N{\fs12}And I don't have to tell you where I was by the seventh grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年级\N{\fs12}Tenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去坐一下豆袋椅\N{\fs12}I'm gonna give the beanbag a whirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在看什么呢\N{\fs12}What are y'all watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《小淘气》\N{\fs12}Little Rascals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}1920-1940年代的系列短片  聚焦一群社区孩子的冒险生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道里面大部分的孩子都死了吧\N{\fs12}You know most of those kids are dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法法  斯代米  巴克威特\N{\fs12}Alfalfa, Stymie, Buckwheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗狗皮蒂也死了吗\N{\fs12}Even Petey the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是狗狗皮蒂\N{\fs12}Oh, especially Petey the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你把这变成致郁片啊\N{\fs12}Thanks for making it depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气\N{\fs12}You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想去吃冰淇淋吗\N{\fs12}Y'all want to go get some ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚饭怎么办\N{\fs12}What about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它呢  走吧\N{\fs12}What about it? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔夫也死了吗\N{\fs12}Is ALF dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没  不过也快了\N{\fs12}No, but it's just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会相信有多少孩子有食物恐惧症\N{\fs12}You'd be surprised how many children have food phobias.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是吗  -是的  我像谢尔顿那么大时\N{\fs12}- Is that so? - Oh, yeah. When I was Sheldon's age,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-很怕布丁上那层奇怪的皮  -真的吗\N{\fs12}- I was afraid of that weird skin on top of puddin'. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  你知道吗  要是覆上一层莎伦牌保鲜膜\N{\fs12}Me, too. You know, you put a little Saran Wrap on...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔治\N{\fs12}George.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿\N{\fs12}Sheldon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑哪儿去了\N{\fs12}Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿\N{\fs12}Sheldon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该走不远\N{\fs12}Couldn't have gone far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  好极了\N{\fs12}Right on, right on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手间和楼梯间我都找遍了\N{\fs12}I checked the bathroom, the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这栋大楼里\N{\fs12}He's not in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心  家里没人接电话\N{\fs12}I'm worried. No one's answering at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持冷静  我们会找到他的\N{\fs12}Stay calm. We'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的时候...\N{\fs12}You know, when I was a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\fs12}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不常独自在都市丛林转悠\N{\fs12}It wasn't typical for me to wander out into
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有任务在身\N{\fs12}the urban jungle on my own, but I was on a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次尝到了超级英雄连载漫画的滋味\N{\fs12}I had gotten my first taste of serialized superheroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}金刚漫画书店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要更多\N{\fs12}and I needed more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  你有《X战警》第137期吗\N{\fs12}Excuse me, do you have X-Men #137?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道接下来的故事  谢了\N{\fs12}I'd like to know what happens next, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角落后面那个箱子\N{\fs12}Back bin in the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来这儿了\N{\fs12}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  丹\N{\fs12}Oh, hello, Tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说漫画是给小孩子看的吗\N{\fs12}I thought you said comic books are for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个复杂的年轻人\N{\fs12}I'm a complicated young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们应该报警\N{\fs12}I think we should call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要出动警察  我们能找到他\N{\fs12}We don't need the police. We'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我的错\N{\fs12}This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑走都是因为我们带他去看心理医生\N{\fs12}He ran away because we took him to a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那15块美金的诊费我们是要不回来了\N{\fs12}That's 15 dollars we ain't getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心的居然是这个吗\N{\fs12}That's what you're worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  当然不是\N{\fs12}No. Course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿不会有事的\N{\fs12}And Sheldon's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道他的个性\N{\fs12}You know what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真有人把他带走了\N{\fs12}If someone took him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定也很快受不了  把他送回来\N{\fs12}I'm sure they'll bring him right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得很开心  但我对里面的拟声词有意见\N{\fs12}I'm enjoying this, but I'm having trouble with the onomatopoeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟什么\N{\fs12}The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拟声词\N{\fs12}The onomatopoeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模拟声音的词\N{\fs12}Words that imitate sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"卡咚"  "口胡"\N{\fs12}KaThoom. SNikt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"砰当"\N{\fs12}BAmf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作家不应该自己乱造词\N{\fs12}Writers shouldn't make up words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"拟声词"就是某人乱造出来的词\N{\fs12}Somebody made up "onomatopoeia". 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挑战我  我喜欢\N{\fs12}You challenge me. I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}冰雪皇后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥  你还会再生小孩吗\N{\fs12}Meemaw, are you gonna have more babies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天啊  我才不要\N{\fs12}Good Lord, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她太老了  生不出来了\N{\fs12}She's too old to have any more babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用生啊  等你活得够老\N{\fs12}Don't have to have 'em. You live long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发和牙齿就开始脱落\N{\fs12}your hair and your teeth start falling out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开始尿床  自己就变成宝宝了\N{\fs12}you start wetting the bed, you get to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真逗\N{\fs12}That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以后要给你穿尿布了\N{\fs12}We're gonna have to put a diaper on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你帮我穿的时候就笑不出来了\N{\fs12}You won't be laughing when you're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可能会笑\N{\fs12}I might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥  除了谢尔顿  我和小乔治谁更聪明\N{\fs12}Hey, Meemaw, next to Sheldon, who's smarter, me or Georgie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-当然是我啦  -为什么\N{\fs12}- Me, of course. - Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脑袋比较大\N{\fs12}My head's bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟头大头小没关系\N{\fs12}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的重点不是谢尔顿\N{\fs12}Tonight is not about Sheldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  平常什么事重点都在谢尔顿身上\N{\fs12}Yeah, right. Everything's always about Sheldon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  大多数时候\N{\fs12}Yeah. Most of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就好像不存在一样\N{\fs12}it's like we don't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢尔顿的确是得到了大部分的关注\N{\fs12}I guess Sheldon does get most of the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但或许这是好事啊\N{\fs12}Maybe that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里好了\N{\fs12}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是有他\N{\fs12}Well, if it weren't for him, 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们爸妈就肯定会严格管着你们俩\N{\fs12}your parents would be on your ass all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  我好像从来没从这角度想过\N{\fs12}Yeah. I guess I never thought about it that way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  要不是有他\N{\fs12}You kidding me? Right now, 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们爸妈现在一定在唠叨让你们打扫房间\N{\fs12}they would be nagging you about cleaning your room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催你们去做作业\N{\fs12}and doing your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在你们能坐在停车场里\N{\fs12}Instead, you're sitting in a parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.21,0:15:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃着冰激凌当晚餐\N{\fs12}eating a Blizzard for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-还加了曲奇面团  -对啊\N{\fs12}- With cookie dough in it. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而谢尔顿却被困在无聊的心理医生办公室\N{\fs12}While Sheldon is stuck sitting in some boring shrink's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈说他们是带他去剪头发\N{\fs12}Mom told me they were taking him for a haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦\N{\fs12}Oh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啦\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等他回家了  记得夸他头发剪得不错\N{\fs12}Well, when he gets home, say his hair looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fs12}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来一根吗\N{\fs12}You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N{\fs12}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...\N{\fs12}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想吃了  你就自己拿\N{\fs12}if you change your mind, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用读太多漫画书\N{\fs12}I didn't have to read many comic books
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道每个英雄都有弱点\N{\fs12}to understand that every superhero had a weakness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}红蜡糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些弱点需要他们靠着\N{\fs12}something they had to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无与伦比的勇气来克服\N{\fs12}through an extraordinary act of courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对镭射眼来说是失去琴·葛雷\N{\fs12}For Cyclops, it was the loss of Jean Grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}全都是《X-战警》的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小淘气来说  则是与人类触碰\N{\fs12}For Rogue, it was human touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说  是需要咀嚼的食物\N{\fs12}For me, it was food that required chewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我真的也是变种人  就得克服难关\N{\fs12}So if I truly was a mutant, I would have to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一天  我不能被打败\N{\fs12}On this day, I would not be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这一天是我变成\N{\fs12}Because this was the day I became...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咀嚼侠的日子\N{\fs12}...The Chewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\pos(192,30)}咔嚼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  我克服了我对被噎到的恐惧\N{\fs12}Just like that, I overcame my fear of choking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一剩下的就只有怕狗\N{\fs12}All that was left was my fear of dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟  昆虫  细菌\N{\fs12}birds, insects, germs,
